=Description=

"Our existing monetary system inspires many rebellions against it. These insurgencies, however, have very different ideological slants, and different assessments about what the problem is, what to change, and what scale to change it at. In this video I cover five of them: state money reformers, bank money reformers, cryptocurrency crusaders, localists and - my current favourite - the crypto-credit alliance."


